The Backstory — fullstackpm.tech
https://www.fullstackpm.tech/resources/the-backstory
One story per weekend — market history, business history, and investor philosophy told as narrative. LTCM, Black Monday, Soros vs the Bank of England, Bezos letters, the dot-com crash. Each episode ends with one lesson that applies to trading or product work today.
